  ('locality-6f0ba476-moex-00479', 'locality-6f0ba476', 'locality-6f0ba476-moex-111-f6c431ec', 'sub-locality-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設社會上僅有 A 與 B 二人，其對某一公共財的個人需求函數分別為 P 100 3Q 與 A A P 200 2Q ，其中P為價格，Q為數量。若提供公共財的邊際成本為200元，在最適公共財的 B B 提供數量之下，下列敘述何者正確？ = −', '["=A與−B二人分別消費40單位與160單位的公共財", "A與B二人分別消費160單位與40單位的公共財", "A與B二人的願付價格分別為40元與160元", "A與B二人的願付價格分別為160元與40元"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a361c6a76a27", "answer_pdf_sha1": "69034777c25d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "314", "s": "1410", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-6f0ba476-moex-00480', 'locality-6f0ba476', 'locality-6f0ba476-moex-111-f6c431ec', 'sub-locality-6f0ba476-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在只有兩個消費者的艾吉渥斯箱型圖（EdgeworthBox）中，不考慮角落解，下列有關交易效率配 置狀態之敘述，何者正確？', '["兩個消費者的效用水準必會相等", "兩個消費者的無異曲線必會相等", "兩個消費者的資源分配必會相等", "兩個消費者的邊際替代率必會相等"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:04+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a361c6a76a27", "answer_pdf_sha1": "69034777c25d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "314", "s": "1410", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
